'''珍妮佛·米雪兒·李'''（Jennifer Michelle Lee，{{bd|1971年|10月22日}}）<ref name=Monn /><ref name=CBChronicleBook>{{cite news|last=Amidi|first=Amid|title=Chronicle Books Is Releasing A Ton Of Cartoon Titles This Fall|url=http://www.cartoonbrew.com/books/chronicle-books-is-releasing-a-ton-of-cartoon-titles-this-fall-61810.html|accessdate=January 5, 2014|newspaper=Cartoon Brew|date=April 26, 2012|archive-date=2014-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141005114046/http://www.cartoonbrew.com/books/chronicle-books-is-releasing-a-ton-of-cartoon-titles-this-fall-61810.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一名美国女性动画电影编剧和导演。代表作品有联合编剧的2012年[[迪士尼动画|迪士尼动画]]《[[无敌破坏王|无敌破坏王]]》以及单独编剧兼联合导演的2013年[[迪士尼动画|迪士尼动画]]《[[冰雪奇缘|冰雪奇缘]]》，后者非常成功口碑为在全球各地收获12.67亿美元的票房佳绩，是有史以来最高票房的动画片。她是迪士尼动画工作室的第一位女性电影导演<ref name=THRBreakSciFi>{{cite news|last=Kit|first=Borys|title='Frozen' Director Wants to Break a Sci-Fi Blockbuster Barrier|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/frozen-jennifer-lee-disney-animation-666372|accessdate=December 31, 2013|newspaper=The Hollywood Reporter|date=December 18, 2013|quote=Lee, 42, is the first woman in the studio's history to act as a director on one of its animated features (she co-directed with Chris Buck).|archive-date=2013-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131223115831/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/frozen-jennifer-lee-disney-animation-666372|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她自2018年起担任[[华特迪士尼动画工作室|华特迪士尼动画工作室]]的首席创意总监。

==生平==
她生于1971年<ref name=LAWQueen>{{cite news|last=Stewart|first=Jill|title=Jennifer Lee: Disney's New Animation Queen|url=http://blogs.laweekly.com/arts/2013/05/jennifer_lee_people_2013.php|accessdate=December 28, 2013|newspaper=LA Weekly|date=May 15, 2013|quote=Raised in East Providence, R.I., Lee, 41, was a flute-playing band nerd who "became a cheerleader — a nerd cheerleader."|archive-date=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230231801/http://blogs.laweekly.com/arts/2013/05/jennifer_lee_people_2013.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=THRBreakSciFi />，母亲和父亲分别为 Linda Lee 与 Saverio Rebecchi<ref name=Monn />，生长于[[罗德岛州|罗德岛州]]的[[普羅維登斯|普羅維登斯]]<ref name=LAWQueen />。获得[[新罕布什尔大学|新罕布什尔大学]]的[[英语|英语]]学位<ref name=AWNDirectorFrozen />，之后到纽约从事[[印刷|印刷]]艺术设计工作<ref name=LAWQueen />。30岁时进入[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]艺术学院学习电影美术<ref name=LAWQueen />，取得艺术创作硕士学位<ref name=AWNDirectorFrozen>{{cite news|last=Wolfe|first=Jennifer|title=Disney Names Jennifer Lee Director Of 'Frozen'|url=http://www.awn.com/news/disney-names-jennifer-lee-director-frozen|accessdate=January 5, 2014|newspaper=Animation World Network|date=November 29, 2012|archive-date=2014-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140112025134/http://www.awn.com/news/disney-names-jennifer-lee-director-frozen|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并遇到了事业搭档 Phil Johnston，后来两人共同担任《[[无敌破坏王|无敌破坏王]]》的编剧<ref name=LAWQueen />。2018年6月，在迪士尼创意总监[[约翰·拉塞特|约翰·拉塞特]]因丑闻宣布离职后，迪士尼宣布珍妮佛·李将接替他在迪士尼的位置。

==个人生活==
1999年她与 Robert Joseph Monn 结婚，后来离婚<ref name=Monn>{{cite web|title=What If Every Day Was Monnday ?|url=http://monn.dyndns.org/|publisher=Monn.org|accessdate=January 5, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140516233444/http://monn.dyndns.org/|archive-date=2014-05-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，两人育有一个生于2003年的女儿 Agatha Lee Monn<ref name=Monn /><ref name=TWSJListenSongs>{{cite news|last=Chai|first=Barbara|title=Listen to Songs From Disney’s ‘Frozen’ and Hear How They Were Written|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2013/11/27/listen-to-songs-from-disneys-frozen-and-hear-how-they-were-written/|accessdate=January 5, 2014|newspaper=The Wall Street Journal|date=November 27, 2013|archive-date=2013-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204131653/http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2013/11/27/listen-to-songs-from-disneys-frozen-and-hear-how-they-were-written/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=LAWQueen /><ref name=THRBreakSciFi /><ref name=Monn />，女儿在2013年电影《[[冰雪奇缘|冰雪奇缘]]》中演唱了一首插曲 "Do You Want to Build a Snowman?"<ref name=THRBreakSciFi />。她目前居住在[[圣费尔南多谷|圣费尔南多谷]]<ref name=LAWQueen />。

